If you are under Windows, add the following block to the file in %USERPROFILE%\Application Data\Subversion\config  
If you are under Linux, add the following block to the file in  ~/.subversion/config  


# BLOCK TO PASTE
[miscellany]
enable-auto-props = yes

[auto-props]
*.c = svn:eol-style=native;svn:keywords=Revision
*.h = svn:eol-style=native;;svn:keywords=Revision
# END OF BLOCK
